Class DamageTypeRanks

java.lang.Object
  org.starhope.appius.game.DamageTypeRanks

public class DamageTypeRanks
extends Object

A collection of damage (or attack, or defence) values. This implements a sort of convenient pseudo-Map, based upon the Map interface.
